HEAT vegetable oil in large skillet over medium-high heat. Add chicken; cook for 3 to 4 minutes or until no longer pink. Add water and seasoning mix. Bring to a boil. Reduce heat to low; cook for 3 to 4 minutes or until mixture thickens SPOON chicken mixture evenly over tortillas. Top with cheese, lettuce, green onions, olives and salsa; fold into burritos.